# 08 â€” KPI Definitions
- **Onboarding Time**: Avg. minutes to complete KYC and activate.
- **Onboarding Completion Rate**: % who start and finish onboarding.
- **Transaction Success Rate**: Successful / total transactions.
- **Engagement**: DAU/MAU, session length, feature adoption.
- **Ticket Deflection**: % of queries resolved by chatbot.

## Targets
- Onboarding Time: -20%
- Transaction Success Rate: +15%
- Engagement: +25%
- Ticket Deflection: +30%
